❄️ Snow-studded serenity, Crisp mountain air and a perfect tent to house it all!
This is winter camping like never before with Abhishek Rawat and the Gipfel Marga One holding strong in the heart of a Himalayan wonderland. 🏔️⛺

From starlit nights to sunrise over snowfields, every moment here is a bucket list ticked off in style.
Would you brave the chill for this kind of thrill?
